This information may help you understand how the state-of-the-art treatment options and expert care at Cancer Treatment Centers of America® (CTCA) can help you achieve your health and life goals.

content.name: section-2
content.textContent: At CTCA®, you receive all your care from a designated team that coordinates the logistics of your treatment. Your team considers your needs, mind, body and spirit, as they recommend innovative treatment options specifically for you. As you progress through treatment, your clinicians help you manage your symptoms and side effects through a multidisciplinary approach.

content.textContent:
Many patients at CTCA benefit from this collaborative approach. On our website you can learn how:
  • CTCA reports patient survival data
  • Care at CTCA impacts patients’ symptoms and daily life
  • Patients rate various aspects of their care at CTCA
  • CTCA performs in terms of patient safety and quality of care

content.textContent: %%FirstName%%, I understand you have important decisions to make, and I want you to know I am here to help. Please take a look at a few of these links and call me to discuss scheduling your evaluation. I can be reached at %%OwnerPhone%% or %%OwnerEmail%%.

content.name: sample-4-Referred
content.textContent: %%FirstName%%, regardless of where you decide to seek cancer treatment, the knowledge you may gain from getting a second opinion can be valuable. Your next step in getting a second opinion at CTCA is to allow me to verify your insurance information. It takes less than 24 hours, so please contact me at %%OwnerPhone%% or %%OwnerEmail%%.
